                    </h3>

                </div>
                <!-- /.card-header -->
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p><b>Laboratory works:</b></p><p>Introduction to logic gates with IC pin details and verify the truth table using bread board.</p><p>1. Use any one simulator to simulate the basic logic circuits functions.</p><p>2. Design of half adder, full adder, subtractor using basic logic gates.</p><p>3. Study and verification of 3-8 decoder using IC.</p><p>4. Study and verification of 8-3 encoder using IC</p><p>5. Implementation of 4-1 Mux using IC</p><p>6. Implementation of 1-4 DeMux using IC</p><p>7. Implementation of 7 Segment Display</p><p>8. Verification of Flip flop</p><p>9. Design and verification of Up counter/Down counter</p><p>10. Design and verification of Shift Register</p><div><br></div>
                </div>
